info.name: github_files-colored
info.description: This style adds a color label to github files to identify easily the extensions. It uses directly the rules defined by the github linguists. As it's semi automated, the version on github is more fresh.
info.additionalInfo: You'd better get the fresh sheet on https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bewam/stylish-github_files-colored/master/stylish-github_files-colored.css. Or build it yourself : https://github.com/bewam/stylish-github_files-colored
